'''亚足联职业级教练员证书'''<ref>{{cite web|title=2012年亚足联中国足联职业级教练员证书强化培训班报名表|url=http://www.fa.org.cn/bulletin/train/2011-12-01/367931.html|work=2011-12-01|publisher=中国足球协会|accessdate=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510232948/http://www.fa.org.cn/bulletin/train/2011-12-01/367931.html|archive-date=2012-05-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>（{{lang-en|'''AFC Professional Coaching Diploma'''}}或{{lang|en|'''AFC Pro-Diploma'''}}），也被称为亚足联P级教练员证书<ref>{{cite news|title=李章洙准备考取P级教练证书 水原三星曾邀请其加盟|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/j/2012-12-20/12046346346.shtml|accessdate=2013-06-15|newspaper=足球|date=2012-12-20|archive-date=2019-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222033602/http://sports.sina.com.cn/j/2012-12-20/12046346346.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是由[[亚足联|亚足联]]颁发的最高级别的足球教练资格证书。亚足联从2001年起颁发这种证书。<ref name="afc1">{{cite web | url=http://www.the-afc.com/en/coaches-news/29800-steady-increase-in-pro-coaching-diploma-holders | title=Increase in pro coaching diploma holders | publisher=Asian Football Confederation | date=2010-07-21 | accessdate=2011-11-03 | archive-date=2013-02-03 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20130203160614/http://www.the-afc.com/en/coaches-news/29800-steady-increase-in-pro-coaching-diploma-holders | dead-url=yes }}</ref>亚足联认为此证书与[[欧足联|欧足联]]颁发的[[欧足联职业级教练员证书|欧足联职业级教练员证书]]等效。<ref name="afc2">{{cite web | url=http://www.afcasiancup.com/en/coaches-news/29787-upgrade-qualification-afc-to-coaches | title=Upgrade qualification: AFC to coaches | publisher=Asian Football Confederation | date=2010-07-20 | accessdate=2011-11-03 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050406/http://www.afcasiancup.com/en/coaches-news/29787-upgrade-qualification-afc-to-coaches | dead-url=no }}</ref>

亚足联规定，要考取亚足联职业级教练员证书的学员必须已经获得[[亚足联A级教练员证书|亚足联A级教练员证书]]。为考取此证书，学员至少接受220小时的培训。<ref name="afc3">{{cite web | url=http://110.74.134.58/en/elite-panel-members- | title=Elite Panel Members | publisher=Asian Football Confederation | date=2008-04-11 | accessdate=2011-11-03 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="afc4">{{cite web | url=http://www.the-afc.com/en/coach-education/coach-education-course-info/29795-4-what-is-the-afc-professional-coaching-diploma-course | title=What is the AFC Professional Coaching Diploma course? | publisher=Asian Football Confederation | date=2010-06-16 | accessdate=2011-11-03 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121207090141/http://www.the-afc.com/en/coach-education/coach-education-course-info/29795-4-what-is-the-afc-professional-coaching-diploma-course | archivedate=2012-12-07 }}</ref>亚足联宣布，2017年起[[亚洲冠军联赛|亚洲冠军联赛]]球队的主教练必须拥有亚足联职业级教练员证书。<ref name="afc3" />

2009年起，[[中国足协|中国足协]]规定在[[中超联赛|中超联赛]]执教的外籍主教练必须凭亚足联职业级教练员证书上岗。2010年，中国足协将规则扩大到所有中超、中甲主教练。[[2010年中甲联赛|2010年中甲联赛]]、[[2011年中超联赛|2011年中超联赛]]和[[2012年中超联赛|2012年中超联赛]]中，[[广州恒大|广州恒大]]的实际主教练[[李章洙|李章洙]]由于未曾考取此证书，无法以主教练身份报名，广州恒大不得不在主教练一栏上先后填上[[李春满|李春满]]和[[金圣求|金圣求]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=李章洙让位李春满 铁帅无证上岗屈居助教职位|url=http://sports.163.com/10/0403/03/63AL829600051C8L.html|accessdate=2013-06-15|newspaper=舜网-济南时报|date=2010-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073850/http://sports.163.com/10/0403/03/63AL829600051C8L.html|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2010赛季中甲联赛广州恒大球员名单|url=http://sports.163.com/10/0401/16/636SSPJ600051C8L.html|accessdate=2013-06-15|newspaper=网易体育|date=2010-04-01|archive-date=2010-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901164851/http://sports.163.com/10/0401/16/636SSPJ600051C8L.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=金圣求|url=http://www.goalchina.net/html/2011/11/07/2011110711160630.htm|accessdate=2013-06-15|newspaper=劲球网|date=2011-11-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130618041743/http://www.goalchina.net/html/2011/11/07/2011110711160630.htm|archivedate=2013-06-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=广州恒大2012赛季中超联赛球员及教练员名单|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/j/2012-03-05/15575968917.shtml|accessdate=2013-06-15|newspaper=新浪体育|date=2012-03-05|archive-date=2013-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130311100247/http://sports.sina.com.cn/j/2012-03-05/15575968917.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2011年中超联赛广州恒大队球员完全名单(3.28)|url=http://sports.sohu.com/20110328/n280035063.shtml|accessdate=2013-06-15|newspaper=搜狐体育|date=2011-03-28|archive-date=2011-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111112145723/http://sports.sohu.com/20110328/n280035063.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

